  "description": "In this very short essay, I explain why I choose to write my name in lowercase.\nWhen I was 12 I joined a server where everyone\u0026rsquo;s name was their first initial and the first four letters of their last name. So my username was \u0026ldquo;msenn.\u0026rdquo;\nAfter a while we migrated systems and the rule was relaxed, and many original members changed their names to be more phonetic—I added an e to the start of mine, to become \u0026ldquo;emsenn.\u0026rdquo;\n",
  "name": "Why emsenn is lowercase",
  "publisher": {
